featured_reviews.review_id:
Alhamdulillah only ahle hadees salafi masjid in entire Bapatla taluka. It's around 80 years old structure mostly in dilapidated condition but prayer area is clean and safe.

People nearby should come to this masjid to learn the true Islam unadulterated and pristine aqeedah and faith related issues.

For travellers, there is a lodge nearby called "Best Lodge" (just search in map)  which is nearby and cheap and rooms are neat and tidy. People from Hyderabad or other districts coming to bapatla for sightseeing beaches like suryalanka anf chirala beach can stay nearby and offer salaah in this masjid. Alhamdulillah.
